- [ ] Android
- [ ] iOS (robovm)
- [ ] iOS (MOE)
- [ ] HTML/GWT
- [x] Windows (Only tested on windows)
- [x] Linux (Does not crash, but the application is hit hard and takes a while to recover)
- [ ] MacOS
